thread.title: Ketchy
thread.title_full: Bake Me A Wish! reviewed by Ketchy

author: Ketchy
title: Ketchy
text: I was skeptical at first but because of the good reviews, I decided to give bakemeawish a try. I ordered a cake for my sister's birthday and there were no hiccups, they delivered just when they said they would!! My sister loved the cake and I would definitely recommend them to anyone!
